Package jellycat.flight.domain.airplane

Class Airplane

  • java.lang.Object
    • jellycat.flight.domain.airplane.Airplane
  • public class Airplane
extends java.lang.Object
    This class holds values pertaining to a single Airplane. Class member attributes are the same as defined by the CS509 server API and store values after conversion from XML received from the server to Java primitives. Attributes are accessed via getter and setter methods.
    Since:
    2019-04-20
    Version:
    1.0 2019-03-16
    Author:
    jellycat
